Business Solutions

Penact Provides Financial Security For Your Business
Penact, a division of Old Point Trust, is engaged exclusively in providing personalized retirement plan design, implementation, administration, plan consulting, and related services for small to medium sized businesses.
In this complex and dynamic area, we are highly trained and pride ourselves in providing quality services while minimizing the burden of paperwork and administrative responsibilities for our clients.
 
Establishing a retirement plan could be one of the smartest business decisions you'll ever make. It can help you gain significant tax advantages as well as providing both you and your employees the secure retirement you've earned.
 
Visit our newsletter library, which is a comprehensive resource for qualified retirement plan information, keeping you abreast of legislative and administrative issues.

 





