Company Overview of Old Point Trust and Financial Services, N.A.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Old Point Trust and Financial Services, N.A. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm also provides financial, estate, and tax strategy planning; estate and trust administration; retirement plan administration; and estate planning services to its clients. It primarily provides its services to individuals, personal trusts, IRA’s, employee benefit plans, foundations, and endowments. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. For its fixed income investments, the firm invests in municipal bonds and corporate bonds. It was formed on April 1, 1999 and is based in Newport News,...
Old Point Trust and Financial Services, N.A. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm also provides financial, estate, and tax strategy planning; estate and trust administration; retirement plan administration; and estate planning services to its clients. It primarily provides its services to individuals, personal trusts, IRA’s, employee benefit plans, foundations, and endowments. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. For its fixed income investments, the firm invests in municipal bonds and corporate bonds. It was formed on April 1, 1999 and is based in Newport News, Virginia with additional offices at Norfolk, Virginia and Virginia Beach, Virginia. Old Point Trust and Financial Services, N.A. operates as a subsidiary of Old Point Financial Corporation.
Detailed Description


